name: NeuropathyDiagnosis
title: Neuropathy Diagnosis
description: This grouper value set is built using existing SCT and ICD10 value sets built by Clinical Architecture.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains diagnosis terms representing neuropathy.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this set of values is to identify patients who have a diagnosis of neuropathy.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes neuropathy diagnosis concepts from  SNOMED CT and ICD-10-CM.),(Exclusion Criteria: None.)
